Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When snow falls into the lake, what happens to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It melts and becomes part of the lake water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, why doesn't it just fall on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow doesn't have a choice where it falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... poor snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, once the lake freezes, \Nthe snow can pile up on top of its ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When will that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as it gets a bit colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope the lake freezes soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:12.91,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an7\bord0\blur0.6\p1\c&H914821&\pos(-2,68)\fscx500\fscy90}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.99,0:03:12.91,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an4\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(120,109)}Beneath the Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be... an inn somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's buried in snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Maybe it's this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I needed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm chilled to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We never have guests at this time of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose the only people \Nwho'd venture through this much snow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,are the really curious ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Well then, what has you so curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the snow itself. It's very interesting around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to come see it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's true we get a lot of snow in these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just typical for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's all that interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir? Your bath is—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going to sleep soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's close this, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, these are drawings of snowflakes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take a look through?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, there are so many different shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a snowflake too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, that one's a type of snow mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sometimes find them if you sift through snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are things like this inside snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're especially diverse in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already found quite a few just around this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Yukinarashi, or a "Snow Smoother" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It lives in the tracks made by animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are enough of these around, \Ntracks made in the snow disappear quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,which can be a nuisance when you're hunting or need to find someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... how about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A Yukidangomushi, or "Snow Roly-poly" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw some on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They move by rolling on top of the snow, making snowballs in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When their snowballs start to get too big,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,they usually crash them against trees to shake off the extra snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you stumble across one with no trees nearby, \Nit may try to crash into you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:05:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They sound pretty mischievous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When they crash into trees, the shockwaves they make sometimes cause avalanches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not as harmless as you might think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What others are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This one here is probably the rarest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This mushi likes to travel in packs \Nand stick close to a specific animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They sting the animal and steal its warmth little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When animals are "possessed" by this type of mushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,snow seems to follow them wherever they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why they're called Tokoyukimushi, or "Never-ending Snow" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What else happens when they possess you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body temperature decreases as well. They say there's no risk of death, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They usually depart when spring comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there someone in particular you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,On your way here, you saw \Nthat house buried in snow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:07:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend lives there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of him that the house became buried in snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Early this winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he lost his little sister to the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too long after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed that snow was always falling around him, and only him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Tae.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten even paler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A mushi-shi named Ginko{-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He was wondering if he could speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for how cold it is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever we try to warm up the place, \Nmy skin starts to hurt... like it's burning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas I don't feel the cold one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How long has it been this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a night with snow but no wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:09:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought for a second that my little sister had come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so I opened the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi—{?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When I did, it felt as though snow had flown right into my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, come back inside, or you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, I can't stand being near anything warm,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,even though the cold doesn't bother me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,From that night on, snow's been falling wherever I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really don't feel cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I do feel bad for Mom and Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's really nothing wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take a look at your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His hand is as cold as ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can't even tolerate human body temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skin's turned white. You're getting frostbite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Although {\i1}you{\i0} may not feel it, your body does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't get yourself warm soon, \Nyou could lose your hands or your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But it really feels like I'm burning when I do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your senses are just being deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not actually burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. I'm fine with the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go catch some fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't figure out how to make him want to get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It stopped snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, something {\i1}is{\i0} wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to do what's best for your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't follow me. It's not safe out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been really out of it lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The snow falling into the lake isn't melting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never knew it could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's the case, maybe snow can pile up \Nat the bottom of the lake too... huh, Sachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The lake's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't—{stand there!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The snow is... only in one spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Did you check over there{ too}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He must be under there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That part of the lake is just too deep. \NWe {just }can't dive there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun's down, too. It's too cold for us to go into the water now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That night, blistering cold descended upon the entire village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a single night, the lake became completely frozen over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not snowing anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a bad feeling that this might happen someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've stopped you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I should never have let you \Ngo out on the lake by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The lake's ice must be contracting and cracking from the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Your mind is playing tricks on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tae{-chan}, Toki's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But he wandered off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He had really bad frostbite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So we tried to warm him up, \Nbut then he ran away like he was burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's split up and find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't treat him soon, it might be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll check the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It really {\i1}is{\i0} you, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get you some help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Sachi's just asleep \Nat the bottom of the lake like I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneath the snow, at the bottom of the lake, I was asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard the ice cracking, I woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she just hasn't woken up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can help her—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, you jumped in after her and dragged her out of the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You held her as she grew colder and colder... \Nuntil she died in your arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not know what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tae... Don't stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Get on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My back is burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tae's heart is still burning hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My cheek stings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see my breath, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My hands and feet hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so cold that I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tae?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps because the scant warmth remaining in Tae's body had warmed him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toki regained normal use of his senses by the time he returned to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the constant snow around him \Nhad somehow stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Both suffered from frostbite, \Nbut Tae's frostbite was fortunately minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toki's was severe. He lost several fingers and toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it was miraculous enough that he returned alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that snow protecting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When I woke up, I was covered in it, \Nas though it were a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it all a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're really leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If I put it off any longer, \NI won't be able to leave till spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You too. Take good care of yourselves until spring comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, winter's only just begun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a land blanketed by white snow throughout most of the year,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it is not the water or the earth,{Comma for "but" emphasis.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the snow that conceals \Nmany of these misshapen entities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come inside and warm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Atop the snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}within the snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and beneath the snow.
